This paper is about fraud detection in online applications, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper proposes a machine learning approach using LSTM-Autoencoder and GAN models, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with analyzing sequences of online activities, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and social networks (cs.SI).
